  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-cluster Kubernetes management from a single interface",
    "AI-powered troubleshooting with OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, DeepSeek, and more",
    "Real-time monitoring of clusters, pods, services, and metrics",
    "Single-binary deployment with zero dependencies",
